Follow these steps to install this product:

1) If you want to use a local copy of the mgiconfig product to configure
   the environment for the install, make sure the MGICONFIG environment
   variable is set to the location of the mgiconfig product that you
   want to use.  Otherwise, the install will look for it in the default
   location (/usr/local/mgi/live/mgiconfig).

2) Copy Configuration.default to Configuration.

3) Run the Install script.
